&lt;p&gt;The Breakdown is about everything funk. It starts with James Brown and takes us on a journey from there - from dusty 70&#x27;s soul 45&#x27;s to heavy Nigerian afro-funk; from fiery Colombian salsa to the bounce of old-school hip-hop; from the deep disco 12&quot;s of underground NYC to the colour and fun of Bollywood funk...&lt;br&gt;
It can all be found right here on PBS every Friday 3-5PM with DJ Manchild.&lt;/p&gt;

